Text: Somebody stayed true to the spirit of the piratebay. Kept on seeding even though when he/she didn't have the full movie. Kudos to you. I hope the original seeder comes back and seeds at least the last .9%. I guess we are all stuck at 99.1% :-) I am going to keep on seeding as a mark of respect to that one seeder whom I had mentioned earlier. And yes the movie can be viewed even though it is only 99.1%. So go ahead and download
